social_posts.post_text: I had the pleasure of meeting @funk_gb during his visit to San Francisco last week, where we took a mini menswear tour of some of the city’s most notable shops. It’s always fascinating how easily generational and international boundaries can be crossed through similar interests. If I wasn’t such a hermit these days, I’d probably do it more often. 😂
It’s all about the wool/silk/linen blends when the temperature rises. 😎🤙🏽
Pretty much everything I like in clothing, all in one look. #tailored#cozy#minimal#streetwear
